Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
CBRE is pleased to exclusively offer for lease, these innovative retail spaces featuring state-of-the-art design, quality finishes and a 6-star energy rating. Be part of Brooklyn Interchange and position your retail business within this exciting strata development including; office tower, service station, strata showrooms and warehouses.

The Brooklyn Interchange is strategically located in Melbourne's inner west, one of Melbourne’s highest growth areas. Boasting direct exposure to Little Boundary Road, and significant frontage to the West Gate Freeway, Western Ring Road and Princes Highway, Brooklyn Interchange offers convenient access to the CBD, the west's major arterials and the port of Melbourne.

With both drive-thru and quick service retail tenancies available, don’t miss this opportunity to position your food offering within this cutting edge commercial and industrial precinct which offers flexible, state-of-the-art spaces with quality finishes and full spectrum of amenities. 

Opportunities available include; 
Drive Thru: 300 sqm*
Retail space; 75 - 85 sqm*

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
CBRE is delighted to offer Brooklyn Interchange Warehouse, 1-11 Little Boundary Road, Laverton North, for lease.

Brooklyn Interchange is the newest industrial, commercial and office development in Melbourne's western suburbs. The project is centrally located, only 150m* from the Princes Highway and 1km* from the West Gate Freeway on/off ramp. 

Available for lease are six large warehouses ranging in size from 1,039sqm* to 4,793sqm*. All warehouses are accompanied by up to 1,800sqm* of secure concrete hardstand each, with additional parking. 

Not only will these warehouses feature their own hardstand, the façade of the buildings will face directly to the Western Freeway/Ring Road/West Gate Freeway interchange. 

Property features:
+ High clearance clear span warehouse
+ Motorised container height RSDs
+ Three phase power
+ Office and amenities over two levels
+ Surplus allocated parking in addition to hardstand
+ 11km* to Port of Melbourne
+ 15km* to Melbourne CBD

For further information or to arrange an on-site inspection, please contact the CBRE team.

*approximate
